# ============================================================
# LOCAL frontend secrets template -- COPY this file to:
#     .env.local        (same folder, gitignored via *.local)
# then fill in your value(s). Everything else (API base URL, feature flag) is
# already provided in the committed .env, so the app runs without this file --
# you only need .env.local to enable Google Maps address autocomplete.
# ============================================================

# Google Maps JavaScript API key (enable "Maps JavaScript API" + "Places API",
# enable billing, and restrict the key to http://localhost:3000). Without it the
# booking address field falls back to a plain text input -- the app still works.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY="your-google-maps-api-key"
